About

taylorswift.com

Taylor Alison Swift is an American singer-songwriter. A subject of widespread public

interest with a vast fanbase, she has influenced the music industry, popular culture,

and politics through her songwriting, artistry, entrepreneurship, and advocacy.

Swift began professional songwriting at 14.

Wikipedia

Born: December 13, 1989 (age 34 years), West Reading, Pennsylvania, United States
Net worth: 1.3 billion USD (2024) Forbes
Height: 1.8 M
Parents: Andrea Swift , Scott Kingsley Swift
Siblings: Austin Swift
